Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.common

Provides all classes for shared MEME objects.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Atom Generically represents an atomic unit of meaning in a Concept.
AtomElement Generically represents something connected to an Atom (and by inheritance, a Concept).
AtomFact Generically represents a connection between two Atoms that is not a formal relationship.
Attribute Generically represents an attribute belonging to either an Atom or a Concept.
Authentication Represents a generic way to allow an Authenticator to provide its authentication information.
Authenticator Generically represents a way to obtain authentication information.
Authority Generically represents an agent responsible for some activity within the MID.
BatchAction Deprecated. Use gov.nih.nlm.meme.action.BatchAction instead
Concept Generically represents a UMLS concept.
ConceptElement Generically represents something connected to a Concept.
ConceptMapping Generically represents a concept mapping.
ContentView Generically represents a Content View.
ContentViewMember Generically represents a content view member.
ContextPath Generically represents a path to the root of a context tree from an Atom.
ContextRelationship Generically represents a parent, child or sibling Relationship.
CoreData Generically represents core data.
CoreDataRestrictor Generically represents a mechanism for restricting CoreData elements of a Concept during retrieval.
EditorPreferences Generically represents information about editors tracked by the system, including their preferences for using the editing interface.
Identifier Generically represents any kind of identifier.
Language Generically represents the language of an Atom.
LoggedAction Deprecated. Use gov.nih.nlm.meme.action.LoggedAction instead
LoggedError Generically represents a logged error.
MapObject Generically represents the identifier or expression of the "to" or "from" of a Mapping.
Mapping Generically represents a mapping between two identifiers or expressions.
MapSet Generically represents a collection of Mappings.
MEMEString Generically represents the strings used for atom names in the MEME database.
Parameter Generically represents a Parameter.
Rank Generically represents a rank.
Rankable Indicates that an object type can be ranked, and provides access to the Rank.
Relationship Generically represents a relationship.
ReportStyle Generically represents a style which is to be applied to an HTML or enscript-enabled concept report.
SearchParameter Generically represents a search criterion.
SemanticType Generically represents a semantic type.
Source Generically represents a UMLS source.
Termgroup Generically represents a termgroup, or a Source, term-type tuple.
Warning Generically represent a warning.
